  "subject": "2.1.5 - fixed getting node-instances from cfy 4.x",
  "commit_message": "2.1.5 - fixed getting node-instances from cfy 4.x\n\n- added _size=1000 to params on getting node-instances from cloudify\n  = cloudify 4.x does not like to have the _offset=0 without _size param\n    cfy assumes that _size=0 and returns no items.\n  = that was working fine in cloudify 3.4\n  = the max _size is now only 1000 in 4.x versus 10,000 in 3.4\n\n- external version 2.1.5, internal version 4.4.5\n- unit test code coverage\nStatements   : 83.99% ( 939/1118 )\nBranches     : 62.75% ( 320/510 )\nFunctions    : 81.15% ( 155/191 )\nLines        : 84.13% ( 928/1103 )\n\nChange-Id: I4c47522c49acc028841c5c08787995f33e7ef0e3\nSigned-off-by: Alex Shatov <alexs@att.com>\nIssue-ID: DCAEGEN2-500\n",
